    <specific name="Power Source"> Primal. </specific>
    <specific name="Creating" />
    <specific name="Class Features" />
    <specific name="Supplemental"> Suggested Combinations

The fighter/warden offers great durability and melee attacks, though this combination might need some help with AC; Warden's Armored Might or Fighter Armor Proficiency are good fixes.

Adding the hybrid cleric gives the hybrid warden useful healing powers; Wisdom is likely your secondary ability.

Combining the hybrid warden with the hybrid ranger increases your damage output without hurting your AC too much. </specific>
    <specific name="Implement" />
    <specific name="Powers" />
    <specific name="Power Name" />
    <specific name="_RoleElement"> ID_FMP_ROLE_4 </specific>
    <specific name="_PowerSourceElement"> ID_FMP_POWER_SOURCE_4 </specific>
    <specific name="_SecondaryPowerSourceElement" />
    <specific name="Secondary Abilities" />
    <specific name="Hybrid Talent Options"> Font of Life, Warden's Armored Might. </specific>
    <specific name="Short Description"> You draw on the primal spirits to protect the natural world from corrupting forces. </specific>
    <specific name="_ParentClass" />
    <specific name="Trait Package" />
    <specific name="_BaseClass"> ID_FMP_CLASS_134 </specific>
    <rules>
      <grant name="ID_INTERNAL_GRANTS_HYBRID_WARDEN" type="Grants" />
